         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Most esteemed Friend, ¶  ¶ […] ¶  ¶ You will be amazed about the many new things that are contained in the last Mueller consignment. I had to point out to Steetz several errors in the revision of the ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">M53.02.04</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From Wilhelm Sonder to Eduard Fenzl</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Archiv der Universität, Vienna.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Verehrtester Freund,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>[…]<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Matter unrelated to M omitted here and elsewhere in the letter.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sie werden erstaunen über die vielen neuen Sachen, die in der letzten Müller'schen Sendung enthalten sind. Unserem guten Steetz muss ich mehere Irthümer der Bearbeitung der Preiss'schen Compositen nachweisen, was mich wundert, da er so bedächtig und ausführlich niederscreibt, er hat sich aber selbst von der Richtigkeit meiner Beobachtungen überzeugt. […]</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Bentham will die Müller'schen [Leguminoseen] vornehmen, was mich sehr freuet; wenn ich nur noch einige Mitarbeiter mehr hätte. Dr Müller ist seit September in Port Philipp u sammelt sehr eifrig, er hat mir schon einige hübsche Sachen geschickt. Er wird jetzt in Gebirge sein, u ohne Zweifel viele der Cunningham'schen Pflanzen auffinden. Stuart sammelt für ihn in einer anderen Gegend.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/> […]</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Herzlichst Ihr</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>W. Sonder</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Hamburg d. 4 Feb. 53</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Most esteemed Friend,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>[…]<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Matter unrelated to M omitted here and elsewhere in the letter.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>You will be amazed about the many new things that are contained in the last Mueller consignment. I had to point out to Steetz several errors in the revision of the Preiss composites, which surprises me since he writes down so thoughtfully and in detail, but he is convinced of the correctness of my observations. […]</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Bentham intends to do the [<name key="Leguminoseae">Leguminoseae</name>], which pleases me very much; if only I had some more co-workers. Dr Mueller has been in Port Phillip since September<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M arrived in Melbourne from SA on 22 August 1852.</p>
               </note> and is collecting very enthusiastically, he has sent me some pretty things already. He will now be in the mountains and undoubtedly will discover many of the Cunningham plants. Stuart is collecting for him in another region.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/> […]</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sincerely your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>W. Sonder</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Hamburg 4 February 1853</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Leguminoseae">Leguminoseae</name>
            </p>
         </div>
